<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>メールアドレスの難読化でスパム対策したい</title>
</head>
<body>
<div>
<p>指定なし<br>
{mailto address='newuser@example.jp'}</p>
<p>hexを指定<br>
{mailto address='newuser@example.jp' encode='hex'}</p>
<p>javascriptを指定<br>
{mailto address='newuser@example.jp' encode='javascript'}</p>
<p>javascript_charcodeを指定<br>
{mailto address='newuser@example.jp' encode='javascript_charcode'}</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
